{"tid":1782807,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聶德權：會研究方便年長和行動不便選民投票的措施","createTime":"2019-12-14T09:41:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T09:41:42.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ca247b0546b4f452e9294e8b8d9ec4fa15e7567c","tid":1782807,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T09:41:01.000Z","msg":"政制及內地事務局局長聶德權表示，會研究方便年長和行動不便的選民投票的措施，希望有人性化的處理，例如在現場情況許可下，安排另一條隊伍輪候投票。聶德權又表示，票站地方有限，會考慮[size=6]<span style=\"color: gold;\">是否限制入場監票的公眾人士數目</span>[/size=6<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />]。<br />\n<br />\n對於有人希望當局實施電子投票，聶德權表示，初步認為電子投票可能有黑客干擾等技術風險，未必會進一步探討，但可以研究電子點票，並希望在明年立法會選舉中，在個別選民數量不太多的功能組別試行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1236807&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1236807%26csid%3D261_341&d=wPrcUaBjKD1L%2BB1JqNzGIBqcspSF5fyAY0%2FEGx5AO9c%3D&h=1c1ee029\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1236807&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"7869b57877eea0cd05c42dff1fa973490e1ea642","tid":1782807,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T09:41:42.000Z","msg":"冇時間啦25號截止，極度要人幫手!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782422</a>"}]}